name: Phylo Gandish (V)
Lore: 'Good-natured former pilot whose family owns a galactic transportation company. Years of travel has her to learn many loopholes in spaceport protocol.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots.  If opponent''s [Virtual Block 6] card just added a destiny to total power or attrition here, draw two destiny, choose one, and subtract it from their attrition and total power.  Your characters here are immune to You Are Beaten and attrition < 3.',
